quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  46,29,"JaŇčto tuma nde Min imminnoo fedde jinna e maa…óa, hi…ói he…óoo Alqur'aana. Nde …ói tawanoo …óum, …ói mbi'i: "He…óee"...Nde [janngin kin] timmunoo, …ói huccitiri ka yim…ďe majji, jeertinooji."
  46,30,"∆äi mbi'i: "eey mon yo mbatu amen, min nanii deftere jippinaande …ďaawo Muusaa, goonginnde …óen adii…óe nde. Hinde feewna e goonga e laawol Pocciingol."
  46,31,"Eey mon yo mbatu amen, nootee noddoowo e Allah on, ngooŇč…óinon mo. [On tuma] O haforanat on bakkatuuji …óiin, O da…ónda on lepte mu'usuu…óe."
  46,32,"Kala mo nootaake noddoowo e Allah on, o wonaa laawotoo…óo ka leydi, o alaa kadi gi…óo ga makko. Ko …ďen ngoni e ndeer majjere …ďanngunde"."
  46,33,"E …ďee nji'aani won'de ko Allah tagi kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndin, O ronkiraani tagugol …ói, won'de ko O kattan…óo wuurnitugol maay…ďe …ďen? Ko non woniri. Pellet, ko O ka…ótan…óo kala hu'unde."
  46,34,"√Ďande he'efer…ďe …ďeen wee…ďitoytee e Yiite ngen, […ďe mbi'anee]: "Wonaa goonga nii?" ∆Āe mbi'a : "Ko non woniri! Min ngo…óondirii Joomi amen!". O Daala : "Awa mee…óiree non lepte …óeen, sabu ko njeddiratno…óon"."
  46,35,"Mu√Ī√Īor mu√Īal joomiraa…ďe pellital …ďeen ka Nulaa…ďe; wota a hawjan …ďe. √Ďande …ďe nji'oyta ko …ďe kammbiranaa kon, …ďe mba'oyat wa si …ďe √Īii…ďaano [ka leydi] si wonaa dumunna-hun √Īalawma. ∆äun ko yottinal. Ko hom…ďe halketee si wonaa yim…ďe faasiqii…ďe …ďeen?"